[Exodus 38:22](../../../bib/kjv/exo038.htm#022.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_022">exo 38:22</span></span>

And Bezaleel the son of Uri, the son of Hur, of the tribe of Judah,....
Of whom and his descent see [Exo 31:2](../../../bib/kjv/exo031.htm#002.md).

made all that the Lord commanded Moses; gave directions about them, and
took care that the tabernacle and all things belonging to it were made,
which the Lord commanded Moses, and in the exact manner in which they
