[Exodus 38:26](../../../bib/kjv/exo038.htm#026.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_026">exo 38:26</span></span>

A bekah for every man, that is, half a shekel, after the shekel of the
sanctuary,.... A half shekel was called a "bekah", from "bakah", to
