second temple, when the hooks, it seems, were iron, but those of the
tabernacle were silver:

and overlaid their chapiters, and filleted them; that is, overlaid the
heads, tops, or knobs of the pillars with silver plates, and filleted,
girded, or hooped other parts of them with silver.

